reviewText: my grandson like this series of videos.
this is a awesome collection of lego ninjago episodes. it is fun and enjoyable to watch. if you have not seen this dvd then i recommend you do

First of all, these two episodes are already on previously released Ninjago dvds--this was a major disappointment to my grandsons.  Secondly, it is extremely overpriced at $19.99.  It is widely available in stores or other websites for $5-6--and even that seems like a ripoff to watch 44 minutes of tv!  The two episodes are good and the boys enjoyed them but I'm sorry I wasted my money.
